   HOLOFIT by Holodiabojana2019-10-08T10:47:00+02:00

   HOLOFIT

   FITNESS. REINVENTED.

   Holodia is the leading VR fitness provider offering multisport
   immersive VR cardio workouts.

   We bring fun, connectivity and competition to your cardio machines:
   bicycles, rowing machines, ellipticals.

   Join HOLOFIT community and row, ride or run in our virtual worlds.

   Compatible with major fitness brands.
   Find out more

   HOLOFIT

   FITNESS. REINVENTED.

   Holodia is the leading VR fitness provider offering multisport
   immersive VR cardio workouts.

   We bring fun, connectivity and competition to your cardio machines:
   bicycles, rowing machines, ellipticals.

   Join HOLOFIT community and row, ride or run in our virtual worlds.

   Compatible with major fitness brands.
   Find out more

   Holodia-environnements-version-finale2 DIVE RIGHT INTO OUR SPECTACULAR
   ENVIRONMENTS [player.png]

MAKE THEM DREAM

   “HOLOFIT VR fitness turns a workout into a vacation”

   (Club Solutions Magazine)

   Attracting new customers and retaining old ones is challenging – and we
   can help you with it!

   HOLOFIT never gets boring – new content, features and workout modes
   keep on coming.
   We offer premium virtual content, virtual coaching and online or local
   competitions.

   Take a step ahead and position your business as the leader of the next
   major fitness revolution!
   Find out more

IMPROVE PERFORMANCE

   With HOLOFIT you reach goals and more – while having fun.

   Whether you are a top athlete looking to improve performance on a
   margin, a regular fitness user or just looking for the right motivation
   tool to start working out and improve your fitness and health, HOLOFIT
   will help get you there!

   HOLOFIT gives you instant access to better fitness, it’s your coach in
   virtual reality or just a connection to anyone in the World that you
   wish to compete or train with.

   The experience is virtual but the results are real!

HOLOFIT App

Take your workouts with you and enjoy your achievements!

   HOLOFIT App with advanced tracking, comparison, competition and
   connectivity features connects you with members
   inside and outside of your gym.

   HOLOFIT trophies, leaderboards, avatar customization and many more
   features will motivate you to
   always come back for more.

